psalm.text:
[[Ps 147,1]]Praise the LORD, for he is good;
sing praise to our God, for he is gracious;
it is fitting to praise him.
[[Ps 147,2]]The LORD rebuilds Jerusalem;
the dispersed of Israel he gathers.

[[Ps 147,3]]He heals the brokenhearted
and binds up their wounds.
[[Ps 147,4]]He tells the number of the stars;
He calls each by name.

[[Ps 147,5]]Great is our LORD and mighty in power:
to his wisdom there is no limit.
[[Ps 147,6]]The LORD sustains the lowly;
the wicked he casts to the ground.
